name: Cuac FM Player for MeeGo
body:
# Cuac FM MeeGo player

This is a player for the streaming service of the [Cuac FM](http://cuacfm.org) community radio
station from A Coru√±a (Spain). The application is designed to work in the Nokia N9 and N950 handsets.

## Support & Development

* **Bug tracking**: https://github.com/aperezdc/cuacfmeego/issues
* **Git repository**: https://github.com/aperezdc/cuacfmeego

## Download

* **At the Ovi Store**: *to be announced*

## Acknowledgments

Thanks to [Igalia](http://igalia.com) for allowing me to invest time in this application, and to all the folks at [Cuac FM](http://cuacfm.org) for their continued hard work.
